    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential for superior power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The suspension retains its factory-spec multi-link geometry with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. While showing minor cosmetic patina, the powertrain remains robust with documented valve adjustments and consistent compression across all cylinders. A purist\u2019s driver with exceptional mechanical fundamentals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
