    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior maintains a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you may find a few minor stone chips on the hood and small surface scratches near the trunk sill consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple and free of tears, though there is light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster from regular use. Every electronic feature, from the responsive infotainment system to the heated seats and dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a comprehensive folder of maintenance receipts included for your review. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The tires are a matching set of Michelins with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a well-loved, reliable vehicle ready for its next owner to drive home with complete peace of mind.",
